<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[وجن]</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>: (} وَجَنَ بِهِ، كوَعَدَ) ،<span class="c5"> {وَجْناً:</span> <span class="c2">(رَمَى.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>(و) وَجَنَ <span class="c2">(بِهِ الأرْضَ)</span> وَجْناً: <span class="c2">(ضَرَبَها بِهِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>(و) وَجَنَ <span class="c2">(القَصَّارُ الثَّوْبُ)</span> وَجْناً: <span class="c2">(دَقَّهُ)</span> ، وَمِنْه} المِيجَنَةُ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">(! والوَجِينُ:</span> شَطُّ الوادِي.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>